{"tid":1174860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警搜交易廣場寫字樓 8人被倫敦金騙過千萬元人民幣","createTime":"2019-05-28T07:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T09:15:29.000Z","uid":3090,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5c701f79f38dc66532f1e288e6f34eb5df391dc2","tid":1174860,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOXwuwu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOXwuwu.png&h=2e7082b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEqBFDa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEqBFDa.png&h=456ddcf0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKCXp4R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKCXp4R.png&h=c6d88ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Wfugbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Wfugbw.png&h=41815fbb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oeb1RKS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeb1RKS.png&h=3bd0cf4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方突擊搜查中環交易廣場一間寫字樓。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n警方突擊搜查中環交易廣場一間寫字樓，撿走一批文件及電腦等證物。警方稱，事件涉及倫敦金騙案，8名事主被騙款項超過千萬元人民幣，而其中一人較早前到集團位於尖沙嘴的寫字樓找晦氣時，更被打傷。警方稍後將交代案情。<br />\n<br />\n讀者盧先生中午時分在交易廣場，見大批警員上高層單位調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，上周二（21日）一名姓李男子（38歲）找晦氣後，在麼地道近港鐵尖東站出入口時，遭6名大漢圍毆。事主雙手護頭縮在地上捱打，另一名左臂有紋身的同黨，則在旁用手機拍下施襲過程。"},{"pid":"a64baa5e01d232cb57f13923e30a3dacc869c34d","tid":1174860,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5c51ed17216c4d64e7b629dfa856af08ad60c0","tid":1174860,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"不如修例監管啦"},{"pid":"061b583ec947e15c2d7e8b4ff919d580